        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "The use of a low-angle shot on the policeman and a high-angle shot on the wagoner conveys a power dynamic of the exchange. The low-angle shot makes the policeman seem menacing and powerful, while the high-angle shot  wagoner seem weak and subordinate to the policeman. It is worth noting, however, the wagoner's face is defiant which suggests a challenge to the policeman's authority.",
